t: "alzanyt walzaani alldhan lm yasbiq lahuma alzwaj, eqwbt kl minhuma miayat jaldat balswt, wathabit fi alsanat mae hdha aljld altghryb limudat eam. wala thmlkm alraft bihima ealaa tarak aleuqubat 'aw tkhfyfha, 'iin kuntum msdqyn biallah walyawm alakhir eamilin bahkam al'islam, wlyhdr aleqwbt eadad min almwmnyn; tshnyeana wzjrana wezt waetbarana"